@startuml HallOrderFSM
title Hall Order FSM

[*] --> Idle
Idle --> Pending : button_press
Pending --> Handling : barrier full /\n calculate cost
Handling --> Arrived : arrived
Arrived --> Idle : barrier full

state Idle : no known order\nlight OFF
state Pending : barrier: nodes that know\nlight OFF
state Handling : cost map by node\nlight ON
state Arrived : barrier: nodes that know served\nlight OFF

' note as n1
' receive_external merge rules:
' - resolve by cyclic precedence
' - pending/arrived: union barrier sets
' - handling: merge cost map (min per node)
' - ensure self in barrier/cost map
' - barrier-full check may advance state
' end note

@enduml
